# Dry Martini

> #gin #cocktail

- Vermouth | Dry, 1/2 oz | 

Fill a mixing glass with ice. Add the vermouth and stir for 10 seconds or so. Dump the vermouth, keeping the ice.

- Gin | 3 oz | 

Add the gin to the mixing glass with the flavored ice cubes and stir for 15 seconds. Strain into a chilled martini glass.

- Lemon | 1 peel | 

Express the oil from a lemon peel into the glass, wipe into onto the rim, and drop it in before serving.
